PidFile run/httpd.pid
Timeout 300

KeepAlive Off

ServerName <%= node[:fqdn] %>

<IfModule worker.c>
StartServers         4
MaxClients         300
MinSpareThreads     25
MaxSpareThreads     75
ThreadsPerChild     25
MaxRequestsPerChild  0
</IfModule>

Listen 80

